{"tid":1555706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行街都隨時被捕，唔該熟讀法例，幫手記錄黑警暴行","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T06:00:16.000Z","uid":117130,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b6122efd79a6494bbc42afbebc80dc044c849e","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">雖然而家警察大晒，唔show委任證，唔跟規矩亂拉人，但係大家都要知道自己嘅權利，盡量記錄警察濫捕、濫權行為，第時可以集體清算。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>首先，要知有咩權利</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第一：關於截停</strong><br />\n<br />\n警察係有權截停你搜查，但係如果警察冇俾適當嘅法律基礎解釋, 可以拒絕合作。<br />\n(但係咁做亦有機會被警察話蓄意阻礙佢哋執行職務，所以有風險。)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二：關於拘捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 警察<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須講到合理地懷疑自己犯咗咩罪</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要求律師陪同</span></strong>下先<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>錄口供</span></strong>。(任何時間，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">切勿同警察/陌生人/被捕人士傾計</span></strong>，因為所講嘅話都可能會被用作不利的證據。)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真係捉咗，有咩可以做/唔做？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 除非警察有搜查令，如果唔係<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">千祈唔好解鎖手機</span></strong>俾警察睇。(注意：為咗防止警察偷睇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手機一定要set密碼</span></strong>，亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好用面容解鎖</strong></span>！)<br />\n<br />\n2. 無論點都好，千祈<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好係未有律師前落口供或者講任何嘢</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警方不合理</span></strong>行事，需要就事件<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做即時記錄</span></strong>。盡量記低細節，之後話俾律師知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每人每日都有機會俾人拉，被捕人士越熟程序，警察濫權嘅風險就越大。<br />\n<br />\n為咗自己，為咗其他義士，唔該大家做好功課，唔好盲目送頭後，俾黑警逍遙法外。<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"439d59eb9ea77efb4c90994c6459e69a0283152f","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a38baf38e7ccd6e5444cf6e24890e56a4a51c019","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:35:43.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"0919b2f70797abd0b5a78786218acbc47b34190b","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c79894501b20fa029d7dbb9596809b8554e57b9e","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2955edc799d16bdf18cc0e27ac6f6542d6d51961","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c2673c8888758d897abdf146e2b51b97464d95a6","tid":1555706,"uid":264996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"（集思廣益）連儂牆唔夠文宣之建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a14c08d442c69176967e32657ac6e3430a6eb083","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:35.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"6a38cd3b6a10cd7744ca31dce3a1155227b18ee0","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"2d729a4580093240956665caee0a6f75a97b4a27","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"0a1e35131767587952ec97b567e3351437b52032","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"e4a2b85a0aac3d1d9e223208931481220b62884a","tid":1555706,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"ade77e1d43918af06aad6b8dbdf04202b931f84f","tid":1555706,"uid":53019